divs: Sighting DetailsIt was a beautiful day in an august of 09' on sabbath and i happened to just get up and walk out the front door and look right at it for some reason. I kept my ufo camera right next to the door on top of a cabinet at that time so i grabbed it as quick as I could, took these seconds of video then as I was refocusing I could not find it anymore, but I could hear it. There was a buzzing hum coming from the object that sounded like a really muffled prop plane
